dc_description_s: Cover title. Title on map: Shiku kaisei Tōkyō zenzu. Publication date on map: Meiji 25 [1892] In Japanese. Oriented with north to the right. Relief shown by hachures. 2 sheets joined Shows views of tourist attractions. Includes address chart by ward [ku] and district [gun], populations, and legend. 1 map: col.; 46 x 68 cm., folded in cover 18 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
